1
00:00:09,760 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ All of my dreams, leading me here ♪

2
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:21,090
♪ Fueling the fire that helped me fight all the fear ♪

3
00:00:22,100 --> 00:00:27,110
♪ All that I've got and all that I am ♪

4
00:00:28,220 --> 00:00:34,240
♪ All that I gave up just to stand where I stand ♪

5
00:00:34,430 --> 00:00:40,100
♪ And every step that I took was towards you ♪

6
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:50,170
Senior,

7
00:00:50,350 --> 00:00:51,280
why are you back?

8
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:53,430
If I hadn't come back,

9
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:56,430
I wouldn't have known you're living so violently now.

10
00:00:56,720 --> 00:00:57,720
Come on,

11
00:00:57,850 --> 00:00:59,060
stop teasing me.

12
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,790
I know you're loyal,

13
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:02,120
which is a good thing.

14
00:01:02,170 --> 00:01:03,630
But you need to be careful.

15
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:06,490
An athlete's body is the most precious thing.

16
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:10,980
This is for you.

17
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:14,150
It's from UCLA.

18
00:01:16,580 --> 00:01:17,920
It's been over a year.

19
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,590
This is your last chance.

20
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:30,520
My mom sent you here to convince me, didn't she?

21
00:01:31,780 --> 00:01:33,240
Does it matter who sent me?

22
00:01:34,289 --> 00:01:36,289
Hasn't this always been your dream?

23
00:01:38,350 --> 00:01:40,479
Don't give up your future

24
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:41,940
for anyone or anything.

25
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:45,190
I'll think about it carefully.

26
00:01:47,660 --> 00:01:48,590
Enough about me.

27
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:50,440
How's married life?

28
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,920
What can I say?

29
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:54,880
Of course it's pretty good.

30
00:01:57,870 --> 00:01:58,710
However,

31
00:01:58,710 --> 00:02:01,570
I heard you've got something new going on recently.

32
00:02:02,020 --> 00:02:03,740
When can I meet this girl?

33
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,940
I really want to know

34
00:02:05,940 --> 00:02:06,350
who managed to

35
00:02:06,350 --> 00:02:08,310
win over young master Jiang.

36
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:12,510
Stop talking about me.

37
00:02:12,530 --> 00:02:13,740
Let's talk about you.

38
00:02:14,140 --> 00:02:16,950
Didn't you also go all in for love?

39
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,960
You were so determined to

40
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,460
go abroad and get married.

41
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:22,230
Well, I'm back now, aren't I?

42
00:02:22,610 --> 00:02:23,050
Yes,

43
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,520
but do you regret

44
00:02:27,390 --> 00:02:28,450
giving up your PhD?

45
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:30,840
I regret it.

46
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:34,590
I regret not finishing school every single day.

47
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:37,160
Now, even if I wanted to go back, I can't.

48
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:40,930
You're just saying that to talk me out of it, right?

49
00:02:40,930 --> 00:02:44,390
From your social media, your life looks pretty good every day.

50
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:47,760
You actually believe everything on social media?

51
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,940
Where's your husband?

52
00:02:54,290 --> 00:02:56,620
Why didn't he come back with you this time?

53
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,660
He has other matters to attend to.

54
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:07,500
[Close to You]

55
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:10,010
[Episode 22: Jiang Bohan, I like you]

56
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:14,130
The 2024 Le'ang Cup Autumn Half-Marathon

57
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:17,040
will be held in Wuhan on October 27th.

58
00:04:17,750 --> 00:04:20,000
The marathon drew a large number of enthusiastic applicants.

59
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:23,400
The lottery results will be announced at the end of the month.

60
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:25,800
Mingxi.

61
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,050
What are you looking at?

62
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:33,390
Running shoes again?

63
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:36,110
You’ve looked at these pairs over and over.

64
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:37,600
Want me to help you pick one?

65
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,800
Actually, I've already made my choice.

66
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:40,880
Then just buy it.

67
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:42,490
I haven’t gotten a spot in the race yet.

68
00:04:42,490 --> 00:04:44,570
Let's wait for the lottery results to come out first.

69
00:04:44,570 --> 00:04:46,030
What were you about to say?

70
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,510
Look,

71
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,220
doesn't this look delicious?

72
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,800
They specialize in mille crepe cakes.

73
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,510
Each slice has over twenty layers.

74
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:54,000
Let’s go try it together, okay?

75
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,750
But

76
00:04:54,770 --> 00:04:56,620
it doesn't look very cheap.

77
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:58,040
I'll treat you.

78
00:04:58,260 --> 00:04:58,990
No need.

79
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,680
It's actually quite simple to make.

80
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,530
If you really want to eat it,

81
00:05:01,530 --> 00:05:02,430
I can make it for you.

82
00:05:02,430 --> 00:05:03,120
Really?

83
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:12,920
Senior,

84
00:05:12,940 --> 00:05:14,140
you're finally back.

85
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,630
From your tone,

86
00:05:16,850 --> 00:05:18,680
why does it sound like you’re here to complain?

87
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,480
Go on, tell me.

88
00:05:19,530 --> 00:05:21,130
What's Jiang Bohan done now?

89
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:24,560
Recently, Jiang Bohan has been completely smitten

90
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,360
by that transfer student at our school.

91
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,220
Because of her,

92
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:29,840
we're not even on speaking terms anymore.

93
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,820
Is it really that serious?

94
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:35,450
So Jiang Bohan doesn't want to go abroad because of her?

95
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,800
Actually, I've never really understood

96
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:42,600
why Jiang Bohan suddenly decided not to go abroad.

97
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,040
After Boyang left,

98
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,620
he started treating me like an enemy.

99
00:05:49,159 --> 00:05:50,070
Anyway,

100
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:53,360
the team already gave him an ultimatum.

101
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,450
This is his last chance.

102
00:05:57,750 --> 00:05:58,240
Senior,

103
00:05:58,390 --> 00:05:59,990
you must try to persuade him.

104
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:03,250
We can't let him give up his future for someone else.

105
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,610
I'll have a good talk with him.

106
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,690
But he's an adult after all.

107
00:06:13,770 --> 00:06:15,500
We have to respect his choices.

108
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:18,110
Let him decide his own life.

109
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,950
He’s not thinking straight right now.

110
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:22,680
If he misses this opportunity,

111
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,880
he'll regret it for the rest of his life.

112
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:46,600
Nian.

113
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:48,159
I've prepared a surprise for you.

114
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:49,620
I'll bring it to you later.

115
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:05,040
[Study abroad exchange and sharing]

116
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:18,830
Oh, what?

117
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:20,630
Wang Chunian?

118
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:21,680
Not bad,

119
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,310
Jie.

120
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,080
Have you confessed yet?

121
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:25,310
Not yet.

122
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,970
You’re actually serious about it?

123
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,600
Of course.

124
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,920
I didn't expect that from you.

125
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:34,180
Aren’t you supposed to be the self-restrained type?

126
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:36,330
Didn’t expect you to slip up like this.

127
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:38,630
Shut up.

128
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:41,920
Want me to help set it up for you?

129
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:42,730
It's a confession.

130
00:07:42,730 --> 00:07:43,860
You need a big group!

131
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:49,159
It's not like you've done it before.

132
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:50,440
This is where you're wrong.

133
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,430
The advisor never

134
00:07:51,430 --> 00:07:52,890
fights on the front lines.

135
00:07:54,810 --> 00:07:55,409
It's over.

136
00:07:56,670 --> 00:07:57,800
Now everyone knows.

137
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:09,750
Good afternoon, students of Jingcai College.

138
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:12,390
Welcome to my sharing session.

139
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:13,680
Well,

140
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,390
some of you may not know me.

141
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,760
You can call me Senior Zihui.

142
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,000
Today,

143
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:22,160
I'd like to share about my experience studying abroad.

144
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:25,510
I hope this will be helpful to you

145
00:08:25,510 --> 00:08:28,000
in your future applications for overseas studies.

146
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,040
Let’s start with a short video.

147
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:56,470
Now, if anyone has any questions,

148
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:57,350
you can ask me.

149
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,080
Senior,

150
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:06,320
can we really ask anything?

151
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:07,480
Of course.

152
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:10,670
But that doesn’t mean I’ll answer everything.

153
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:11,670
Okay.

154
00:09:11,990 --> 00:09:12,590
Well,

155
00:09:12,790 --> 00:09:13,550
may I ask,

156
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,390
how do you confess to a girl you like?

157
00:09:20,410 --> 00:09:22,770
It depends on what kind of girl she is.

158
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:25,480
But I think regardless of how you do it,

159
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:27,790
sincerity is the most important thing.

160
00:09:27,930 --> 00:09:30,460
He Shuhao, who are you planning to confess to?

161
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:31,460
No one.

162
00:09:31,930 --> 00:09:33,290
I'm asking for a friend.

163
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,730
Any more questions?

164
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,700
It's your birthday today.

165
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:42,380
I booked a restaurant for tonight

166
00:09:42,380 --> 00:09:43,710
and invited Senior too.

167
00:09:43,730 --> 00:09:44,610
Just show up.

168
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:46,670
Thank you,

169
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:48,290
but no need.

170
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,660
But you haven't celebrated your birthday in two years.

171
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:54,120
Senior finally came back,

172
00:09:54,370 --> 00:09:56,170
we should at least get together.

173
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,000
I said,

174
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:00,430
no need.

175
00:10:04,650 --> 00:10:05,770
If you want,

176
00:10:07,060 --> 00:10:08,720
you can also invite Yu Mingxi.

177
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,170
Don’t say another word.

178
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,300
Does anyone else have a question?

179
00:10:19,270 --> 00:10:21,330
How long do you plan to stay this time?

180
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,860
I'll be staying for quite a while this time.

181
00:10:26,860 --> 00:10:27,830
About a month.

182
00:10:32,860 --> 00:10:33,360
Alright.

183
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,660
That concludes today's talk.

184
00:10:34,660 --> 00:10:35,860
Thank you, everyone.

185
00:10:54,770 --> 00:10:55,700
Long time no see.

186
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,360
How have you been lately?

187
00:10:58,580 --> 00:10:59,910
Life abroad,

188
00:10:59,930 --> 00:11:01,590
it's just like that, isn't it?

189
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:22,730
Qin Siyao!

190
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:24,120
Why’d you throw my cake?

191
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,360
Cake?

192
00:11:25,950 --> 00:11:26,620
I'm sorry,

193
00:11:26,770 --> 00:11:28,030
I thought it was trash.

194
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:29,350
You did it on purpose.

195
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,030
Don't bother.

196
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:33,480
Jiang Bohan doesn't like these little tricks.

197
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:35,480
What nonsense are you talking about?

198
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,670
It's just a cake, isn't it?

199
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:37,320
How much was it?

200
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,840
I'll compensate you later.

201
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,370
Don't go.

202
00:11:39,470 --> 00:11:40,170
Explain yourself clearly.

203
00:11:40,170 --> 00:11:41,700
I have nothing to say to you.

204
00:11:48,410 --> 00:11:49,670
Yu Mingxi, you savage!

205
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:56,090
Qin Siyao, you've provoked me today.

206
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:01,720
Yu Mingxi!

207
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:07,380
Let go!

208
00:12:16,410 --> 00:12:17,180
Let go!

209
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:18,500
You let go first!

210
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:19,560
What are you doing?

211
00:12:19,860 --> 00:12:20,650
Let go!

212
00:12:22,170 --> 00:12:22,900
Jiang Bohan!

213
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,090
Yu Mingxi hit me!

214
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,850
You just can't keep up the act anymore, can you?

215
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:26,670
What act are you talking about?

216
00:12:26,670 --> 00:12:27,910
You threw my cake first,

217
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:28,790
and pushed me!

218
00:12:28,790 --> 00:12:29,390
Pay me back for the cake!

219
00:12:29,390 --> 00:12:30,240
You need to compensate me for my bracelet!

220
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,910
Can you even afford to compensate me?

221
00:12:31,910 --> 00:12:32,440
Alright!

222
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:33,270
I'll pay for it.

223
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:34,870
You pay me for the cake first!

224
00:12:35,570 --> 00:12:36,130
Here you go.

225
00:12:36,130 --> 00:12:37,030
Just string it back together.

226
00:12:37,030 --> 00:12:38,510
How can it be the same after stringing it back together?

227
00:12:38,510 --> 00:12:40,570
You compensate me for the cake first!

228
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:41,270
Fine.

229
00:12:41,390 --> 00:12:42,200
You're trying to extort money from me, aren't you?

230
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:42,670
How much?

231
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:43,640
I'll compensate you.

232
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,630
I made that myself.

233
00:12:44,630 --> 00:12:46,360
You compensate me with an identical one!

234
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:48,030
If you made it, it’s even more worthless!

235
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:48,720
Who are you calling worthless?

236
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,790
I’m calling you worthless!

237
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:50,850
You're worthless!

238
00:12:51,390 --> 00:12:51,750
You!

239
00:12:52,030 --> 00:12:53,090
You're worthless!

240
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,270
Jiang Bohan, let me go!

241
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:54,910
Let go!

242
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,020
You're worthless!

243
00:12:56,020 --> 00:12:57,090
Don't pull me!

244
00:13:00,710 --> 00:13:01,370
Here you go.

245
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:08,750
You’re going too far.

246
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:10,670
I picked it up for you out of kindness.

247
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:12,200
It's none of your business.

248
00:13:12,910 --> 00:13:14,580
Mingxi made that cake for me.

249
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:16,130
It wasn't for Jiang Bohan.

250
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:18,750
The more you play these little tricks,

251
00:13:18,830 --> 00:13:20,490
the closer those two will get.

252
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:22,930
What about you then?

253
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,870
Always hanging around the basketball team,

254
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:25,800
clinging to him.

255
00:13:25,970 --> 00:13:27,700
You think you're not annoying?

256
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:30,750
Aren't you always hovering around Jiang Bohan too?

257
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:31,870
What right do you have to criticize me?

258
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:33,380
At least I have more right than you do.

259
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:33,980
Qin Siyao,

260
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:36,170
you don't need to take it out on her.

261
00:13:36,170 --> 00:13:37,100
I'm not leaving.

262
00:13:37,820 --> 00:13:38,960
Your temper is so bad,

263
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,730
and your tongue is so sharp.

264
00:13:39,730 --> 00:13:41,190
You're way more annoying.

265
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:43,140
Stop acting like you’re all that.

266
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,330
Your dancing is so poor,

267
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,880
and your body's out of shape.

268
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:48,430
You still dare to eat cake?

269
00:13:49,070 --> 00:13:51,930
I've never seen such a thick-skinned girl like you.

270
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:53,550
Every day, apart from acting cute and being boy-crazy,

271
00:13:53,550 --> 00:13:54,680
what else can you do?

272
00:13:55,090 --> 00:13:56,490
No one will ever like you.

273
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:57,270
Qin Siyao.

274
00:13:58,510 --> 00:13:59,440
Don't go too far.

275
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:07,480
Are you okay?

276
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,090
It's alright.

277
00:14:11,090 --> 00:14:12,290
It's fine, it's fine.

278
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:21,420
Jiang Bohan, where are you taking me?

279
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:24,860
Let go!

280
00:14:25,800 --> 00:14:26,840
It's not my fault.

281
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:27,870
Why are you pulling me outside?

282
00:14:27,870 --> 00:14:29,000
If I don't pull you, who should I pull?

283
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,360
Should I pull Qin Siyao instead?

284
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:30,870
