306
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:25,130
What exactly is our relationship?

307
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:29,290
The two of us...

308
00:15:29,290 --> 00:15:31,550
What kind of relationship could we have?

309
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:35,230
You don't want to say it, huh?

310
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:37,100
Forget it.

311
00:15:37,710 --> 00:15:38,910
