313
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:45,270
Jiang Bohan!

314
00:15:45,380 --> 00:15:50,710
♪ Fueling the fire that helped me fight all the fear ♪

315
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:56,950
♪ All that I've got and all that I am ♪

316
00:15:57,790 --> 00:16:03,070
♪ All that I gave up just to stand where I stand ♪

317
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,130
I like you!

318
00:16:03,850 --> 00:16:09,890
♪ And every step that I took was towards you ♪

319
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:14,300
Then I'll think about it.

320
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:19,560
♪ I never thought I'd have it all ♪

321
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:26,320
♪ But everything's changed and anything's possible ♪

322
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:25,910
Are you jealous?

323
00:16:26,740 --> 00:16:30,050
♪ I found what I've been looking for ♪

324
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:33,200
No need to change your shoes.

325
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:50,960
This is...

326
00:16:51,910 --> 00:16:52,910
Probably,

327
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,460
when You Jingchu left,

328
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:55,240
he was in a hurry,

329
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:55,600
so he

330
00:16:55,980 --> 00:16:56,910
made such a mess.

331
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:58,680
It's okay.

332
00:17:02,510 --> 00:17:04,109
He's quite tidy, huh?

333
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:09,460
