340
00:17:30,950 --> 00:17:31,350
Right!

341
00:17:31,570 --> 00:17:32,500
Hold on a second.

342
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,890
The cake you gave to Wang Chunian today,

343
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:48,440
